    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're zipping through your daily commute or heading out on a fun weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you! It runs smoothly, looks great, and is just waiting for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 28900.0,
