    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically robust, with the critical double-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its sharp turn-in characteristics, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains a masterpiece of atmospheric engineering, providing a raw, tactile connection to the road that modern platforms struggle to replicate.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
