    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a blend of reliability and refined aesthetics. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine and smooth body lines, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use that do not detract from its impressive curb appeal. Step inside to a cabin that has been treated with respect; the premium upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard remains crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs strong and quiet, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule that ensures a confident and responsive driving experience. It is a turn-key car that has been loved by its previous owner and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
