      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape and ready for many more miles of memories. It runs like a dream and has been super dependable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-cared for while still being a total steal. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so I've priced it to move! Drop me a message if you want to come see it in person\u2014I'd love to show you around your potential new ride!",
